===Personal pronoun===
'''ты''' (ty)

# second-person singular, nominative case: [[you]], [[thou]]
#:'''''Usage note:''' The personal pronoun '''''ты''''' is comparable to French ''tu'', German ''du'', and is used only with family and intimate friends. In classical literature, it is used by superiors to their inferiors, but that usage is no longer tolerated. For most occasions, the formal '''''[[вы]]''''' should be used instead.

